    <item>
      <title>菲律宾抨击中国在音频索赔问题上“严重违规”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/philippines-slams-china-for-serious-breaches-over-audio-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾国家安全顾问表示，据称中国外交官与菲律宾军方官员之间的通话录音“不应未经批准就被放行”，并要求立即驱逐所有涉案人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/philippines-slams-china-for-serious-breaches-over-audio-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:26:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
